  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7524583/" class="title-link">语言有点像马克思的辩证论述</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7524583"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2737103/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2737103-37.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2737103/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">哈哈儿</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-07-09"
      class="main-meta">2015-07-09 09:06:58</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7524583_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  大量的类比和反转。 很多类似马克思“就德国来说，对宗教的批判基本上已经结束；而对宗教的批判是其他一切批判的前提。”、“批判的武器不能替代武器的批判”等的句式。 还有“谬误在天国为神祗所作的雄辩[oratio pro aris et focis①]一经驳倒，它在人间的存在就声誉扫地了。...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
